# No API keys required.
#
# This app runs entirely on free, open services — no registration needed:
#   - Nominatim (OSM geocoding):  nominatim.openstreetmap.org
#   - Overpass API (POI data):    overpass-api.de
#   - OpenStreetMap (map tiles):  openstreetmap.org
#   - Wikipedia (descriptions):   en.wikipedia.org
#
# Just run:  npm install && npm run dev
